WEBVTT

00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:03.790
Well, good evening family or good

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:05.950
morning wherever you are.

00:00:05.960 --> 00:00:08.190
Thank you for joining us again tonight.

00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:10.510
I'm going to just pray a little bit and

00:00:10.520 --> 00:00:13.350
pray over New Year's Eve and

00:00:13.360 --> 00:00:16.550
whatever

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:17.910
they want to talk

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:19.550
about. I'll answer some questions, I

00:00:19.560 --> 00:00:21.910
guess. But we have one little thing that

00:00:21.910 --> 00:00:21.920
will

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:24.190
show you what I believe is a

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:26.630
result of prayer. And I think that

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:31.110
God is so amazing to me as we see

00:00:31.120 --> 00:00:34.110
the news before the news comes on. And

00:00:34.120 --> 00:00:36.230
I want to say this:

00:00:36.240 --> 00:00:39.150
we give all the glory to Jesus.

00:00:39.160 --> 00:00:41.550
I

00:00:41.560 --> 00:00:44.150
want you to know how much I depend on

00:00:44.160 --> 00:00:45.150
him

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:46.750
and how much when people say, 'Bren, you

00:00:46.760 --> 00:00:50.350
say I a lot.'It's just

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:52.110
speech.

00:00:52.120 --> 00:00:54.110
It's not about me.

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:56.070
This is all about him.

00:00:56.080 --> 00:00:59.390
And everything I do in word and in

00:00:59.390 --> 00:00:59.400
deed,

00:00:59.400 --> 00:01:01.950
I give all to the glory of God.

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:04.310
I hope you all know that. I can't make

00:01:04.320 --> 00:01:06.110
this happen;

00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:08.350
it's all the Holy Spirit.

00:01:08.360 --> 00:01:12.070
I

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.510
don't know how else to

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:15.990
say it. There's no possible way to do

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:17.470
this in the natural.

00:01:17.480 --> 00:01:20.950
It's all the Holy Spirit. And so

00:01:20.960 --> 00:01:22.510
it's such an honor that he would even

00:01:22.520 --> 00:01:23.830
look my direction

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:25.870
and want me to even pray and do this on

00:01:25.870 --> 00:01:25.880
a

00:01:25.880 --> 00:01:28.550
live stream and pray with y'all and

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.870
do this YouTube channel like we do. And

00:01:31.880 --> 00:01:35.270
it's been amazing. We went back and

00:01:35.280 --> 00:01:36.910
looked at all the things that the Lord

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:39.430
has told us to pray over this year.

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:41.670
And oh, what a year we've had

00:01:41.680 --> 00:01:43.310
as we get ready to close out this

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:45.950
beautiful year. There's only four days

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:47.230
left

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:48.430
and

00:01:48.440 --> 00:01:50.070
I'm just so grateful for every single

00:01:50.080 --> 00:01:51.470
one of you.

00:01:51.480 --> 00:01:53.030
There's so many of you that

00:01:53.040 --> 00:01:55.430
have been so faithful in coming

00:01:55.440 --> 00:01:58.390
and watching. Some of you

00:01:58.400 --> 00:02:00.470
showed me what YouTube

00:02:00.480 --> 00:02:02.390
gives you—what you watch

00:02:02.400 --> 00:02:05.390
the most at the end of

00:02:05.390 --> 00:02:05.400
the year—and

00:02:05.400 --> 00:02:07.470
I was in your top percentage of

00:02:07.480 --> 00:02:09.749
everything that you watch on YouTube.

00:02:09.759 --> 00:02:12.150
I thought, 'What an

00:02:12.150 --> 00:02:12.160
honor.'It's

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:13.870
all about Jesus. I know you're not

00:02:13.880 --> 00:02:15.710
here to watch Brandon;

00:02:15.720 --> 00:02:17.870
you're here because we pray and

00:02:17.880 --> 00:02:19.510
I believe we're going to get

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:21.870
results. I believe the power of prayer

00:02:21.880 --> 00:02:24.070
changes things and so do you, or you

00:02:24.080 --> 00:02:25.950
wouldn't be here either.

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:27.790
But

00:02:27.790 --> 00:02:27.800
that's

00:02:27.800 --> 00:02:29.710
pretty amazing, huh?

00:02:29.720 --> 00:02:31.230
So in New Orleans,

00:02:31.240 --> 00:02:33.310
that was one of the major

00:02:33.320 --> 00:02:35.470
highlights and we'll go over that. I

00:02:35.480 --> 00:02:38.030
feel in my spirit to go over

00:02:38.040 --> 00:02:39.811
what the Lord showed us.

00:02:39.880 --> 00:02:42.710
He pointed out the night we

00:02:42.720 --> 00:02:44.150
went right in and I was getting ready to

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:45.990
take communion. If

00:02:45.990 --> 00:02:46.000
anybody

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:49.230
remembers watching that video,

00:02:49.240 --> 00:02:50.910
the moment I was getting

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:52.910
ready to take the blood,

00:02:52.920 --> 00:02:54.590
I went into the spirit and I saw

00:02:54.600 --> 00:02:56.670
New York again.

00:02:56.680 --> 00:02:58.910
I saw the flash;

00:02:58.920 --> 00:03:02.030
it looked like drones. It

00:03:02.040 --> 00:03:04.110
looked like some kind of a drone attacked.

00:03:04.110 --> 00:03:04.120
I heard

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:06.310
people screaming

00:03:06.320 --> 00:03:09.070
again. I heard women screaming.

00:03:09.080 --> 00:03:11.150
It was at the point where

00:03:11.160 --> 00:03:13.350
I heard the

00:03:14.560 --> 00:03:17.470
song

00:03:17.470 --> 00:03:17.480
'Imagine'playing.

00:03:17.480 --> 00:03:19.870
I remember

00:03:19.880 --> 00:03:21.510
in the vision everything was so clear. I

00:03:21.520 --> 00:03:23.510
could see the flash, but I don't know

00:03:23.520 --> 00:03:25.630
what would cause something of that

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:27.550
magnitude of a flash.

00:03:28.600 --> 00:03:29.830
As

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.470
we were praying, then I was taken

00:03:31.480 --> 00:03:33.670
to New Orleans and the people—it was

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:35.910
down Bourbon Street. I could see Bourbon

00:03:35.920 --> 00:03:37.550
Street again. I could see people with

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:39.510
black hoodies on,

00:03:39.520 --> 00:03:42.270
and it was where

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:44.550
the horse and the church in the

00:03:44.560 --> 00:03:46.190
background was, and where they sell

00:03:46.200 --> 00:03:47.510
beignets

00:03:47.520 --> 00:03:51.350
by the river right there.

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:53.230
He specifically brought up the Sugar

00:03:53.240 --> 00:03:56.510
Bowl on New Year's Day

00:03:56.520 --> 00:03:57.830
to pray over. I believe it's New

00:03:57.840 --> 00:03:59.750
Year's Day, either the first or the second,

00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:01.750
but I believe it's the first.

00:04:01.760 --> 00:04:03.630
Oh, the Sugar Bowl.

00:04:03.630 --> 00:04:03.640
Yes,

00:04:03.640 --> 00:04:05.830
the first.

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:08.470
Praying over the Sugar Bowl in New

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:11.390
Orleans. But isn't it interesting that

00:04:11.400 --> 00:04:12.990
they even bring it up and

00:04:13.000 --> 00:04:15.110
they're asking for help because they're

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:16.789
getting tips?

00:04:16.799 --> 00:04:19.030
Did he say

00:04:19.040 --> 00:04:21.590
they caught somebody down there?

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:23.310
They said they had a threat.

00:04:23.320 --> 00:04:25.350
I heard that. It

00:04:25.360 --> 00:04:26.470
actually sounded like they found

00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:27.070
somebody.

00:04:27.080 --> 00:04:28.670
I was trying to follow

00:04:28.670 --> 00:04:28.680
because

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:29.670
that was the first time I'd seen that, and

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:31.590
I was like, 'Hey, it looks like they

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:34.510
got one.'And so I believe that's

00:04:34.520 --> 00:04:36.510
the beginning of an unraveling. This is

00:04:36.520 --> 00:04:38.310
what we're praying over.

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:40.150
Can you play that one more

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.630
time? I just wanted to hear that. I

00:04:42.640 --> 00:04:44.830
was trying to catch that because I

00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:44.840
never heard it.

00:04:44.840 --> 00:04:46.950
I was like,

00:04:46.950 --> 00:04:46.960
'Wow.'So

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:49.190
they stopped somebody at border

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:50.830
patrol,

00:04:50.840 --> 00:04:52.550
an extremist. So that's kind of

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:53.710
interesting.

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:56.030
I wonder what it has to do with New

00:04:56.040 --> 00:04:59.510
Orleans. But you know, I thought,

00:04:59.520 --> 00:05:00.830
when the Lord spoke to us

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:04.070
specifically about

00:05:04.070 --> 00:05:04.080
semi-trucks

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:06.390
running into crowds,

00:05:06.400 --> 00:05:08.510
it wasn't vans.

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:12.910
It was big trucks, like big dump trucks,

00:05:12.920 --> 00:05:15.230
trying to use

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:17.870
a big duty

00:05:17.870 --> 00:05:17.880
truck—a

00:05:17.880 --> 00:05:19.630
big, big truck.

00:05:19.640 --> 00:05:21.590
Not like these little,

00:05:21.600 --> 00:05:22.790
you know, like a little Hyundai or

00:05:22.800 --> 00:05:24.190
something. I'm talking about this truck

00:05:24.200 --> 00:05:26.790
was armored and it was ready.

00:05:26.800 --> 00:05:29.510
And it goes back to what the Lord showed

00:05:29.520 --> 00:05:30.670
us. You know, I was praying over

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:33.310
the

00:05:33.310 --> 00:05:33.320
fifty-gallon

00:05:33.320 --> 00:05:35.910
drum vans

00:05:35.920 --> 00:05:38.030
with all of the fertilizer, and the Lord

00:05:38.040 --> 00:05:39.510
kept telling us, 'Remember Timothy

00:05:39.510 --> 00:05:39.520
McVeigh?'Sorry,

00:05:39.520 --> 00:05:41.270
I keep itching my nose.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:43.430
I've been outside in the yard praying,

00:05:43.440 --> 00:05:45.630
and

00:05:45.630 --> 00:05:45.640
the

00:05:45.640 --> 00:05:47.070
dirt and stuff makes me

00:05:47.080 --> 00:05:50.070
itch. I

00:05:50.070 --> 00:05:50.080
even

00:05:50.080 --> 00:05:51.630
got dirt all over my fingers

00:05:51.630 --> 00:05:51.640
because

00:05:51.640 --> 00:05:53.694
I was playing in the dirt.

00:05:55.240 --> 00:05:56.750
I love nature.

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:01.150
The Lord was reminding me of

00:06:01.160 --> 00:06:02.950
everything that he showed us this time

00:06:02.960 --> 00:06:06.310
last year concerning the inauguration

00:06:06.320 --> 00:06:09.630
when we were praying for the

00:06:09.630 --> 00:06:09.640
fifty-gallon

00:06:09.640 --> 00:06:12.510
drums and I saw vans full of

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:14.910
fertilizer. And the Lord said, 'Remember

00:06:14.920 --> 00:06:17.710
Timothy McVeigh.'I truly believe those

00:06:17.720 --> 00:06:19.310
are not gone.

00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:22.110
I truly believe the fertilizer and all

00:06:22.120 --> 00:06:24.150
the things that the Lord showed me, from

00:06:24.160 --> 00:06:27.510
the detail of the money exchange

00:06:27.520 --> 00:06:30.070
coming from overseas from a

00:06:30.080 --> 00:06:33.510
certain country funding this—that this

00:06:33.520 --> 00:06:35.910
was a

00:06:35.910 --> 00:06:35.920
multi-million

00:06:35.920 --> 00:06:38.110
dollar operation that didn't just go

00:06:38.120 --> 00:06:39.630
away.

00:06:39.640 --> 00:06:42.510
I saw those vans full of fertilizer,

00:06:42.520 --> 00:06:45.990
black barrels full of fertilizer.

00:06:46.920 --> 00:06:49.310
There were huge barrels all in the

00:06:49.320 --> 00:06:51.510
back, and then I saw dump trucks

00:06:51.520 --> 00:06:54.150
full of fertilizer.

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:55.670
And the Lord said, 'Remember Timothy

00:06:57.350 --> 00:06:57.360
McVeigh.'So

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:02.270
as I was in the yard today,

00:07:02.280 --> 00:07:04.990
I was still praying and interceding for

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:08.350
those dump trucks and those vans.

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:09.870
And

00:07:09.880 --> 00:07:11.550
I'm telling you all that we should be on

00:07:11.550 --> 00:07:11.560
heightened

00:07:11.560 --> 00:07:13.230
alert. You should pray.

00:07:13.240 --> 00:07:15.510
I don't know when,

00:07:15.510 --> 00:07:15.520
but

00:07:15.520 --> 00:07:17.550
the Lord said it would be a Red Dawn

00:07:17.560 --> 00:07:19.310
experience. He keeps bringing those

00:07:19.320 --> 00:07:21.910
things up to me. Praying over the storm,

00:07:21.920 --> 00:07:24.390
the enemy within,

00:07:24.400 --> 00:07:27.110
an infiltration into our

00:07:29.200 --> 00:07:31.750
homeland security kind of stuff. Praying

00:07:31.760 --> 00:07:34.470
for our FBI. Praying for our

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:36.950
local law enforcement. Praying for our

00:07:36.960 --> 00:07:38.390
churches

00:07:38.400 --> 00:07:40.190
because the Lord brought it up. He said,

00:07:40.200 --> 00:07:42.430
'Don't forget, Bren.'He brings

00:07:42.440 --> 00:07:44.670
all these things to me. And Diana,

00:07:44.680 --> 00:07:46.630
thank God for her taking notes.

00:07:49.600 --> 00:07:52.270
She keeps all those notes for me

00:07:52.280 --> 00:07:53.710
and writes all the things down that the

00:07:53.720 --> 00:07:56.990
Lord tells us—even about

00:07:59.200 --> 00:08:01.950
casing churches, casing amusement parks,

00:08:01.960 --> 00:08:04.670
praying over Disney World, praying over

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:08.110
Las Vegas when I saw the major truck

00:08:08.120 --> 00:08:10.790
driving down. And then there was

00:08:10.800 --> 00:08:14.470
actually a knifing in Paris.

00:08:14.470 --> 00:08:14.480
Braden

00:08:14.480 --> 00:08:17.230
told me that, well, we saw

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:19.110
that because there was not a

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:21.550
lot of access to firearms, they

00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:24.670
would have knifings. I saw slashers

00:08:24.680 --> 00:08:29.070
in vans going down the road and

00:08:29.080 --> 00:08:31.510
jumping out and going into major crowds

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:33.510
and just going after

00:08:33.520 --> 00:08:35.149
people.

00:08:35.159 --> 00:08:38.149
I saw three men in particular going into

00:08:38.159 --> 00:08:40.589
a public area in France.

00:08:40.599 --> 00:08:43.110
So we pray for those things. We saw

00:08:43.120 --> 00:08:45.870
somebody already with this identical

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:48.550
style of attack.

00:08:49.240 --> 00:08:52.190
I don't know if she made

00:08:52.190 --> 00:08:52.200
it—the

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:54.710
person

00:08:56.400 --> 00:08:59.230
he cut up.

00:08:59.240 --> 00:09:01.190
Well, we pray they did. But

00:09:01.200 --> 00:09:02.870
this is the kind of

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:04.910
stuff the Lord's been warning us about,

00:09:04.920 --> 00:09:06.910
and it was in Paris, the exact place we

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:08.470
prayed over.

00:09:08.480 --> 00:09:11.470
So, did it happen with a van? No. But

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:13.870
this is exactly what: 'French police

00:09:13.880 --> 00:09:17.030
arrest suspect after three stabbings in

00:09:17.040 --> 00:09:19.270
Paris metro attack.'So he was in a

00:09:19.280 --> 00:09:20.950
train.

00:09:20.960 --> 00:09:23.030
He's doing it the same way the Lord

00:09:23.040 --> 00:09:25.750
told us they were going to.

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:25.760
"Where

00:09:25.760 --> 00:09:27.790
are

00:09:27.790 --> 00:09:27.800
my

00:09:27.800 --> 00:09:30.790
children?"They

00:09:30.790 --> 00:09:30.800
were

00:09:30.800 --> 00:09:34.590
running

00:09:34.590 --> 00:09:34.600
through

00:09:34.600 --> 00:09:36.630
the

00:09:36.630 --> 00:09:36.640
streets

00:09:36.640 --> 00:09:39.190
looking

00:09:39.190 --> 00:09:39.200
for

00:09:39.200 --> 00:09:42.710
their

00:09:42.710 --> 00:09:42.720
kids.

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:44.550
They had

00:09:44.550 --> 00:09:44.560
pictures;

00:09:44.560 --> 00:09:46.510
they had everything in their hands. "Do you see him?

00:09:46.510 --> 00:09:46.520
Do you know where he is? Have you seen him?"And

00:09:46.520 --> 00:09:48.110
they were asking everybody, "Have you seen him?"This was going on because all the children from the age of 15 down to newborns were completely gone. I asked the Lord about that. He said that is the age of accountability. Then he said, "Brandon, all the others who don't know me will be left."I saw all of this that I'm showing to you. Go ahead, you can play some of it. I filmed it because the town we lived in at the time is where I was taken

00:09:49.190 --> 00:09:49.200
to

00:09:50.840 --> 00:09:52.510
in

00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.710
the

00:09:58.390 --> 00:09:58.400
future.

00:10:02.430 --> 00:10:02.440
I

00:10:04.480 --> 00:10:06.670
want

00:10:08.150 --> 00:10:08.160
to

00:10:11.470 --> 00:10:11.480
show

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:16.750
you.

00:10:19.400 --> 00:10:21.950
This is a football field that's right down from the courthouse. Everyone brings their Bibles in because the Antichrist tells everyone they have to bring their Bibles to the courthouses. At the courthouse I showed you down that street, where I was at the beginning of it, they later bring all their Bibles, and there are stacks

00:10:21.950 --> 00:10:21.960
of Bibles everywhere. The Antichrist forces you to, and then they bring them to this football field right here. It's called Jelsma Stadium. They burn them by the tens of thousands, stacked a story high—a huge fire in the middle of this field. You see that green field? That's going to be one in the future.

00:10:21.960 --> 00:10:27.630
I saw it

00:10:27.630 --> 00:10:27.640
burning,

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:28.910
full of

00:10:28.910 --> 00:10:28.920
Bibles.

00:10:28.920 --> 00:10:31.750
This is a video I made several years ago. It’s a bowl-like stadium, really deep, and

00:10:31.750 --> 00:10:31.760
it shows how big the stack of Bibles is. It's similar to when Hitler

00:10:31.760 --> 00:10:35.110
burned all the books and Bibles. You saw it during Indiana Jones, and that’s

00:10:35.110 --> 00:10:35.120
similar to what I saw when I was standing with Jesus when they burned

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:36.510
them. I saw the smoke go up for miles. You can see it from

00:10:36.510 --> 00:10:36.520
