00:27:06.960 --> 00:27:09.110
will you reap. It's even scripture. If

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:11.030
you sow a thimbleful, you're going to

00:27:11.040 --> 00:27:13.230
reap a thimble. If you sow a dump

00:27:13.240 --> 00:27:15.790
truck, you're going to reap dump trucks.

00:27:15.800 --> 00:27:17.870
If you sow a vineyard, you're going to

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:24.150
reap vineyards.

00:27:24.160 --> 00:27:25.669
But people make it complicated and

00:27:25.679 --> 00:27:27.550
think, 'Well, I'm qualified, so

00:27:27.560 --> 00:27:29.790
XRP is going to make it happen for

00:27:29.800 --> 00:27:31.030
me.'And

00:27:31.040 --> 00:27:34.230
I go, 'Okay, but even if it did

00:27:34.240 --> 00:27:36.230
and you put your money into it, are you

00:27:36.240 --> 00:27:38.310
going to keep it? Will it be riches

00:27:38.320 --> 00:27:40.270
without sorrow, or will you lose it

00:27:40.270 --> 00:27:40.280
all?''Well,

00:27:40.280 --> 00:27:42.710
I won the lottery,

00:27:42.710 --> 00:27:42.720
brother.'But

00:27:42.720 --> 00:27:44.110
that's just a game of chance. I'm

00:27:44.120 --> 00:27:45.350
talking about walking in spiritual

00:27:45.360 --> 00:27:46.870
authority and law.

00:27:46.880 --> 00:27:48.150
I don't believe in chance. I don't play

00:27:48.160 --> 00:27:49.350
the lottery.

00:27:49.360 --> 00:27:51.150
I don't do scratch-offs. Back in

00:27:51.150 --> 00:27:51.160
the day,

00:27:51.160 --> 00:27:52.790
it was

00:27:52.800 --> 00:27:54.070
fun—every

00:27:54.080 --> 00:27:54.990
once in a while, I'd go,

00:27:55.000 --> 00:27:56.190
'Oh yeah, they got that $5

00:27:56.200 --> 00:27:57.710
scratch-off

00:27:57.710 --> 00:27:57.720
ticket,'and

00:27:57.720 --> 00:27:59.350
if I won something, I'd take the kids

00:27:59.360 --> 00:28:01.390
out and get an ice

00:28:01.390 --> 00:28:01.400
cream—but

00:28:01.400 --> 00:28:03.990
I don't look at

00:28:03.990 --> 00:28:04.000
games

00:28:04.000 --> 00:28:06.070
of chance. I put my hand to something,

00:28:06.070 --> 00:28:06.080
and

00:28:06.080 --> 00:28:07.830
whatever I put my

00:28:07.840 --> 00:28:10.390
hands to, the Lord blesses.

00:28:10.400 --> 00:28:12.790
I don't look for

00:28:12.790 --> 00:28:12.800
a

00:28:12.800 --> 00:28:15.190
mailbox mentality faith.

00:28:15.190 --> 00:28:15.200
I'm

00:28:15.200 --> 00:28:16.510
always looking for a miracle in the

00:28:16.520 --> 00:28:17.950
mailbox.

00:28:17.960 --> 00:28:21.669
Whatever I put my hands to will prosper.

00:28:21.679 --> 00:28:24.590
I ask God to bless my hands.

00:28:24.600 --> 00:28:27.510
I ask God to bless my mind. Show me,

00:28:27.520 --> 00:28:30.510
Lord, where to do things. And I'll be

00:28:30.520 --> 00:28:32.470
driving down the road—I kid you not, it's

00:28:32.470 --> 00:28:32.480
something

00:28:32.480 --> 00:28:33.750
we talk about all the

00:28:33.750 --> 00:28:33.760
time—and

00:28:33.760 --> 00:28:35.470
I'll be praying in the Holy Spirit.

00:28:35.480 --> 00:28:36.590
He says, "You see that land right

00:28:36.600 --> 00:28:37.669
there?

00:28:37.679 --> 00:28:40.230
It just came up for

00:28:40.230 --> 00:28:40.240
sale."And

00:28:40.240 --> 00:28:42.149
in the natural, I know I

00:28:42.159 --> 00:28:44.590
can't buy it. I don't have it. But He's

00:28:44.600 --> 00:28:46.270
talking to me about things, stretching

00:28:46.280 --> 00:28:47.430
me,

00:28:47.440 --> 00:28:49.390
making me believe for more.

00:28:49.400 --> 00:28:51.149
And in the natural, the money is not there

00:28:51.159 --> 00:28:53.190
to buy it, but He talks to me about it.

00:28:53.200 --> 00:28:54.630
He says, "Brandon, that piece of land

00:28:54.640 --> 00:28:56.630
right there in the next couple of

00:28:56.640 --> 00:28:58.430
years is going to be worth tens of

00:28:58.440 --> 00:29:01.470
millions of

00:29:01.470 --> 00:29:01.480
dollars."I

00:29:01.480 --> 00:29:03.230
said, "Wow,

00:29:03.240 --> 00:29:04.750
that's awesome.

00:29:04.760 --> 00:29:06.870
Praise God. It's worth a million dollars

00:29:06.880 --> 00:29:08.790
right

00:29:08.800 --> 00:29:09.830
now."So

00:29:09.840 --> 00:29:12.710
I look it up and sure enough,

00:29:12.710 --> 00:29:12.720
a

00:29:12.720 --> 00:29:14.310
couple of years later, just like He

00:29:14.320 --> 00:29:17.230
said, a developer bought it. He put

00:29:17.240 --> 00:29:18.390
houses on it. It's worth tens of

00:29:18.400 --> 00:29:19.990
millions

00:29:20.000 --> 00:29:22.390
just like the Lord said.

00:29:22.400 --> 00:29:24.230
And I look at those things and I

00:29:24.240 --> 00:29:26.510
grow. It helps me to grow because I

00:29:26.520 --> 00:29:30.390
realize it helps get that trust level up,

00:29:30.400 --> 00:29:32.909
because one day He's going to talk and I'm

00:29:32.909 --> 00:29:32.919
going to

00:29:32.919 --> 00:29:34.230
have the money and I'm going to

00:29:34.240 --> 00:29:35.630
buy that land. I'm going to do what He

00:29:35.640 --> 00:29:38.190
said, and you can take it

00:29:38.200 --> 00:29:40.790
to the bank. God will bless your hands.

00:29:40.800 --> 00:29:45.030
Why? Because I practice His presence.

00:29:45.040 --> 00:29:47.910
I don't look to Him as

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:50.710
a genie in the bottle. "Oh God, Holy

00:29:50.720 --> 00:29:51.870
Ghost,

00:29:51.870 --> 00:29:51.880
you're

00:29:51.880 --> 00:29:53.310
like my genie in a little bottle right here.

00:29:53.320 --> 00:29:54.910
My oil.

00:29:54.920 --> 00:29:56.630
Tell me what it is. Let me have the

00:29:56.640 --> 00:29:57.870
lottery numbers,

00:29:57.880 --> 00:29:59.070
lucky

00:29:59.080 --> 00:30:01.030
snake eyes 77 or whatever."And you got it.

00:30:01.030 --> 00:30:01.040
"And

00:30:01.040 --> 00:30:02.350
Lord, we're going to make

00:30:02.350 --> 00:30:02.360
it."No,

00:30:02.360 --> 00:30:04.590
it's

00:30:04.600 --> 00:30:05.710
flaky.

00:30:05.720 --> 00:30:07.430
I look at it. I sow the seed. I say,

00:30:07.440 --> 00:30:10.350
"Father, I spend time with you."And

00:30:10.350 --> 00:30:10.360
in the

00:30:10.360 --> 00:30:13.230
least expected times and in unlikely

00:30:13.240 --> 00:30:15.830
ways, He talks.

00:30:15.830 --> 00:30:15.840
I'll

00:30:15.840 --> 00:30:16.950
be outside in the yard pulling

00:30:16.950 --> 00:30:16.960
weeds—and

00:30:16.960 --> 00:30:18.870
I don't have weeds right now

00:30:18.870 --> 00:30:18.880
because

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:20.190
it's winter,

00:30:20.200 --> 00:30:22.550
but I'd still go outside

00:30:22.560 --> 00:30:24.830
and even move a rock around,

00:30:24.840 --> 00:30:25.910
just sitting out there. That's what I did

00:30:25.920 --> 00:30:27.110
today. I

00:30:27.110 --> 00:30:27.120
sit

00:30:27.120 --> 00:30:29.350
out there and I listen

00:30:29.360 --> 00:30:31.310
because He'll talk whenever your mind is

00:30:31.320 --> 00:30:35.670
off of your problems.

00:30:35.680 --> 00:30:37.110
Think about how you can pray for

00:30:37.120 --> 00:30:39.310
somebody else today.

00:30:39.320 --> 00:30:40.990
Think about how you can maybe pray for

00:30:41.000 --> 00:30:42.630
your loved ones. Like I was

00:30:42.640 --> 00:30:43.870
praying for my mom and my dad; they're

00:30:43.880 --> 00:30:45.550
going through hard times. You listen

00:30:45.560 --> 00:30:48.070
to people and you

00:30:48.080 --> 00:30:49.750
take your eyes off of yourself for a

00:30:49.760 --> 00:30:51.870
minute and pray for somebody else in

00:30:51.880 --> 00:30:54.470
their need, and God will speak to you

00:30:54.480 --> 00:30:55.590
and He'll correct you a lot of the

00:30:55.590 --> 00:30:55.600
time.

00:30:55.600 --> 00:30:56.470
He'll correct me: "You

00:30:56.480 --> 00:30:58.270
shouldn't have said that.

00:30:58.280 --> 00:31:00.030
None of your business.

00:31:00.040 --> 00:31:01.670
You don't need to say that."And I wasn't

00:31:01.680 --> 00:31:03.790
even looking for what He said.

00:31:03.800 --> 00:31:05.910
But He'll talk in the most

00:31:05.920 --> 00:31:07.750
unlikely way. You'll be

00:31:07.750 --> 00:31:07.760
like, "Well,

00:31:07.760 --> 00:31:09.350
look at that.

00:31:09.360 --> 00:31:11.630
I wasn't even asking for that. But thank

00:31:11.640 --> 00:31:12.630
you."And

00:31:12.640 --> 00:31:14.990
I don't just cast it aside. I listen

00:31:15.000 --> 00:31:16.950
to it and I take note of it. I get my

00:31:16.960 --> 00:31:19.190
phone out and I use the voice recorder

00:31:19.200 --> 00:31:21.590
because I look at everything He

00:31:21.600 --> 00:31:24.110
says as precious.

00:31:24.120 --> 00:31:25.630
No matter if I was looking for the

00:31:25.640 --> 00:31:28.270
answer or not, I take those times

00:31:28.270 --> 00:31:28.280
to

00:31:28.280 --> 00:31:30.550
go, "Thank you, sir. Thank you,

00:31:30.560 --> 00:31:33.510
Father. Thank you for taking the time to

00:31:33.520 --> 00:31:36.310
correct me. For you correct those that

00:31:36.320 --> 00:31:39.990
you

00:31:39.990 --> 00:31:40.000
love."And

00:31:40.000 --> 00:31:42.550
Father, you'll teach me how to make

00:31:42.560 --> 00:31:45.790
the bigger money when I can handle it.

00:31:45.800 --> 00:31:47.430
If I'm not able to handle it and it

00:31:47.440 --> 00:31:49.670
would destroy me and cost me my marriage

00:31:49.680 --> 00:31:52.830
or cost me my children, then

00:31:52.840 --> 00:31:54.550
Father, I thank you that you build the

00:31:54.560 --> 00:31:57.550
character in me.

00:31:59.920 --> 00:32:01.830
But if I don't have the character to

00:32:01.840 --> 00:32:03.550
handle it,

00:32:03.560 --> 00:32:05.350
then Father, I thank you, Lord, that you

00:32:05.360 --> 00:32:07.310
create in me a clean heart, that I'm able

00:32:07.320 --> 00:32:09.150
to do what I need to do,

00:32:09.160 --> 00:32:10.550
and thank you, Lord, that I'm a good

00:32:10.560 --> 00:32:12.950
steward of what you've given me. And you

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:16.230
can stretch this dollar until

00:32:16.240 --> 00:32:22.150
it looks like a rubber band,

00:32:22.160 --> 00:32:24.950
or the quarter, or whatever you've got.

00:32:24.960 --> 00:32:27.270
But I know that if I can sow my

00:32:27.280 --> 00:32:29.750
offering into good ground,

00:32:29.760 --> 00:32:31.750
into your church where you're

00:32:31.750 --> 00:32:31.760
going—and

00:32:31.760 --> 00:32:33.190
if your church doesn't have

00:32:33.200 --> 00:32:38.270
good ground, why are you going there?

00:32:38.280 --> 00:32:40.630
I always check it. Check the ground.

00:32:40.640 --> 00:32:43.310
Check the pastors. Check it

00:32:43.320 --> 00:32:46.350
first. Tithe and then sow.

00:32:46.360 --> 00:32:48.190
But don't dump your load of

00:32:48.200 --> 00:32:49.870
seed into something

00:32:49.880 --> 00:32:51.630
until you at least check the ground to

00:32:51.640 --> 00:32:54.350
see where you're sowing into.

00:32:54.360 --> 00:32:57.030
And if you start seeing a turnaround

00:32:57.040 --> 00:32:59.230
and you start seeing increase, then you

00:32:59.240 --> 00:33:01.310
give a little bit more

00:33:01.320 --> 00:33:02.910
and you sow a little bit more. But then

00:33:02.920 --> 00:33:05.310
if you see a cankerworm on it,

00:33:05.320 --> 00:33:08.310
first check your heart.

00:33:08.320 --> 00:33:10.150
Check your marriage. Make sure there's

00:33:10.160 --> 00:33:12.990
no strife, because faith works by love.

00:33:13.000 --> 00:33:15.350
Keep the main thing the main

00:33:15.360 --> 00:33:18.710
thing. Keep the relationship vertical. If

00:33:18.710 --> 00:33:18.720
you

00:33:18.720 --> 00:33:20.350
go horizontal and look at all this other

00:33:20.360 --> 00:33:22.470
stuff,

00:33:22.480 --> 00:33:23.830
it's not always the church's fault.

00:33:23.830 --> 00:33:23.840
You've

00:33:23.840 --> 00:33:25.390
got to make sure that you're in the

00:33:25.400 --> 00:33:26.630
right place at the right time doing

00:33:26.640 --> 00:33:28.270
exactly what He asked you to do and

00:33:28.280 --> 00:33:30.150
sowing where He tells you to sow, being

00:33:30.160 --> 00:33:32.950
obedient. For instance, I was going to

00:33:32.960 --> 00:33:35.350
sow my seed for my sacrificial gift

00:33:35.360 --> 00:33:37.230
this year, and I was going to give it

00:33:37.240 --> 00:33:39.390
back at Christmas time to the

00:33:39.390 --> 00:33:39.400
minister,

00:33:39.400 --> 00:33:41.270
and

00:33:41.270 --> 00:33:41.280
the

00:33:41.280 --> 00:33:43.710
Lord said,

00:33:43.710 --> 00:33:43.720
"No."I

00:33:43.720 --> 00:33:45.710
said, "Why? You don't want me to give

00:33:45.720 --> 00:33:46.669
it all?

00:33:46.679 --> 00:33:48.630
I'll give it somewhere else because, Lord,

00:33:48.640 --> 00:33:51.390
I want to bless your ministry.

00:33:53.160 --> 00:33:54.470
Let me do this. You don't want me to

00:33:54.480 --> 00:33:55.710
do

00:33:55.710 --> 00:33:55.720
that?"He

00:33:55.720 --> 00:33:57.590
said, "Not

00:33:57.590 --> 00:33:57.600
yet."I

00:33:57.600 --> 00:33:59.430
said, "But I'd like to get it in there

00:33:59.440 --> 00:34:01.550
and celebrate at

00:34:01.550 --> 00:34:01.560
Christmas."Just

00:34:01.560 --> 00:34:03.390
celebrating You because I'm giving it

00:34:03.400 --> 00:34:06.270
to You. I don't give it to the minister;

00:34:06.280 --> 00:34:09.510
I give it to Jesus because it's His.

00:34:09.520 --> 00:34:11.149
I don't give it for kudos from the

00:34:11.159 --> 00:34:12.349
person;

00:34:12.359 --> 00:34:15.070
I give it to Jesus so He goes, "Well

00:34:15.080 --> 00:34:16.750
done,

00:34:16.750 --> 00:34:16.760
Brandon."I

00:34:16.760 --> 00:34:18.110
don't give it so they'll look and say,

00:34:18.120 --> 00:34:19.550
"Well, thank you for that

00:34:19.560 --> 00:34:22.430
extra money, sir. I appreciate that.

00:34:22.440 --> 00:34:25.310
Oh, good job,

00:34:25.310 --> 00:34:25.320
Brandon."I

00:34:25.320 --> 00:34:27.909
give it so Jesus looks at me and says

00:34:27.919 --> 00:34:30.030
it was the heart. Even if they don't

00:34:30.040 --> 00:34:33.710
even acknowledge you, I gave it to Him.

00:34:33.720 --> 00:34:36.790
It was His Christmas; it's His birthday.

00:34:36.800 --> 00:34:39.430
I sow into the birthday.

00:34:39.440 --> 00:34:40.470
Let me bless you with a birthday

00:34:40.480 --> 00:34:42.310
present.

00:34:42.320 --> 00:34:44.149
Why? The harvest of souls—that's all He

00:34:44.159 --> 00:34:45.590
cares about.

00:34:45.600 --> 00:34:47.510
He's the Lord of the harvest. So

00:34:47.520 --> 00:34:50.550
he said to me, "No,

00:34:50.560 --> 00:34:52.389
don't give it."And I thought, "Oh no,

00:34:52.399 --> 00:34:55.710
there must be something wrong.

00:34:55.720 --> 00:34:58.670
Am I in control or You?

00:35:00.960 --> 00:35:02.630
When do you want me to give

00:35:02.630 --> 00:35:02.640
it?""I

00:35:02.640 --> 00:35:05.670
want you to do it on the 27th.""On the 27th?

00:35:09.590 --> 00:35:09.600
Okay."So

00:35:12.080 --> 00:35:13.870
I told Diana, "We're holding off

00:35:13.880 --> 00:35:15.349
on that. We're not going to give it at

00:35:15.349 --> 00:35:15.359
all."She

00:35:15.359 --> 00:35:16.790
goes,

00:35:16.800 --> 00:35:18.349
"I don't care, honey. We've

00:35:18.359 --> 00:35:19.190
already talked about that. We're going

00:35:19.200 --> 00:35:21.349
to sow. We're believing God for 2026.

00:35:21.359 --> 00:35:23.349
Let's go and get it in

00:35:23.359 --> 00:35:24.510
the ground. The faster it's in the ground, the

00:35:24.520 --> 00:35:27.510
faster the harvest is."I said, "No, the

00:35:27.520 --> 00:35:29.150
Lord said wait until the 27th."She goes,

00:35:29.150 --> 00:35:29.160
"Well,

00:35:29.160 --> 00:35:31.790
I know you hear the

00:35:31.790 --> 00:35:31.800
Lord."That's

00:35:31.800 --> 00:35:33.950
interesting.

00:35:33.960 --> 00:35:35.830
So I

00:35:35.840 --> 00:35:38.670
waited until I could do it today. And

00:35:38.680 --> 00:35:40.270
I was so excited about it because I told the

00:35:40.280 --> 00:35:42.830
Lord, "I'm giving it for my 2026

00:35:42.840 --> 00:35:44.349
increase.

00:35:44.359 --> 00:35:47.110
I'm believing for my 2026 increase. I'm

00:35:47.120 --> 00:35:49.349
believing for our ministry to not have

00:35:49.359 --> 00:35:51.190
any lack, not anything, and that whatever

00:35:51.200 --> 00:35:52.790
you tell us to do to grow our ministry

00:35:52.800 --> 00:35:54.830
in 2026, we're going to have more than

00:35:54.830 --> 00:35:54.840
enough."So

00:35:54.840 --> 00:35:56.390
I

00:35:56.390 --> 00:35:56.400
sow

00:35:56.400 --> 00:35:59.390
it.

00:35:59.400 --> 00:36:01.790
I went today and I got to put it in

00:36:01.800 --> 00:36:03.150
there. And I felt the

00:36:03.160 --> 00:36:05.430
anointing all over it. And I pray over

00:36:05.440 --> 00:36:06.790
it just like we always do. Anoint it

00:36:06.800 --> 00:36:07.910
with oil,

00:36:07.920 --> 00:36:10.510
pray over it, take communion,

00:36:10.520 --> 00:36:13.310
release it by faith. We take it as a family,

00:36:13.320 --> 00:36:15.230
all laying hands on it, praying over

00:36:15.240 --> 00:36:17.110
the envelope as we put it in the

00:36:17.120 --> 00:36:20.550
mailbox to go and deliver it

00:36:20.560 --> 00:36:24.430
because I want it. David didn't give

00:36:24.440 --> 00:36:28.070
anything that didn't cost him something.

00:36:28.080 --> 00:36:30.950
Everything David gave, it cost him

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:32.430
something.

00:36:32.440 --> 00:36:33.990
He even talked about it because they

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:35.470
were going to give the sacrifice and he

00:36:35.480 --> 00:36:37.150
said, "No, no, no. It has to cost me

00:36:37.160 --> 00:36:38.790
something. I'm only going to give

00:36:38.800 --> 00:36:42.190
something that cost me

00:36:42.200 --> 00:36:44.110
something."So

00:36:44.120 --> 00:36:46.990
it makes your flesh squirm.

00:36:47.000 --> 00:36:48.470
When it makes your flesh squirm, it's

00:36:48.480 --> 00:36:50.030
uncomfortable.

00:36:50.040 --> 00:36:51.590
And that's what we do.

00:36:51.600 --> 00:36:53.830
And we do it every year. Some

00:36:53.840 --> 00:36:56.590
years I go, "Oh God, I thank

00:36:56.600 --> 00:36:59.190
you for

00:36:59.190 --> 00:36:59.200
this."God

00:36:59.200 --> 00:37:01.990
loves a cheerful giver.

00:37:02.000 --> 00:37:04.510
So you help out the people that God

00:37:04.520 --> 00:37:06.870
tells you to.

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:09.750
That's why I always say

00:37:09.760 --> 00:37:11.950
it's easy for me to come at you and say

00:37:11.960 --> 00:37:13.910
all this because we never ask for

00:37:13.920 --> 00:37:15.390
anything.

00:37:15.400 --> 00:37:17.310
I'm telling you this out of

00:37:17.320 --> 00:37:20.510
instruction so you can learn.

00:37:20.520 --> 00:37:21.910
And you say, "Brandon, it's

00:37:21.920 --> 00:37:23.270
about your

00:37:23.270 --> 00:37:23.280
ministry."No.

00:37:23.280 --> 00:37:25.750
I'm not teaching you

00:37:25.760 --> 00:37:28.110
this to sow to me;

00:37:28.120 --> 00:37:30.230
I'm teaching this so that you'll learn

00:37:30.240 --> 00:37:33.390
how to grow in your ministry and what God's called

00:37:33.400 --> 00:37:35.870
you to do.

00:37:35.880 --> 00:37:37.790
Do you understand? I hate

00:37:37.800 --> 00:37:39.310
manipulation,

00:37:39.320 --> 00:37:42.070
especially in churches

00:37:42.070 --> 00:37:42.080
and

00:37:42.080 --> 00:37:44.510
big ministries.

00:37:44.510 --> 00:37:44.520
There

00:37:44.520 --> 00:37:45.910
is

00:37:45.920 --> 00:37:48.349
a lot of manipulation,

00:37:48.359 --> 00:37:50.790
especially in the Word of Faith circles.

00:37:50.800 --> 00:37:53.030
I look at it and say you can keep

00:37:53.040 --> 00:37:56.110
it and use it for whatever

00:37:56.120 --> 00:37:57.790
the Lord tells you to do.

00:37:57.800 --> 00:37:59.349
I don't think a preacher should ever be

00:37:59.359 --> 00:38:02.470
manipulating people. It's wrong,

00:38:02.480 --> 00:38:04.630
especially using the platform.

00:38:04.640 --> 00:38:07.790
Follow the Holy Ghost and do what He tells

00:38:07.800 --> 00:38:10.470
you to do.

00:38:10.480 --> 00:38:12.590
Mary said, "Whatever He tells you to

00:38:12.600 --> 00:38:15.230
do, do

00:38:15.230 --> 00:38:15.240
it."Obey.

00:38:15.240 --> 00:38:19.230
Fill the water pots

00:38:19.230 --> 00:38:19.240
with

00:38:19.240 --> 00:38:21.550
water, and He turned the water into wine.

00:38:21.560 --> 00:38:26.190
Whatever He tells you to do, do it.

00:38:26.200 --> 00:38:27.990
Don't listen to the man of God tugging

00:38:28.000 --> 00:38:30.630
at your heart with emotional violins.

00:38:32.680 --> 00:38:34.310
"Won't you help

00:38:34.310 --> 00:38:34.320
me?"No,

00:38:34.320 --> 00:38:37.590
keep your money.

00:38:37.600 --> 00:38:41.390
Follow the voice of God for your life.

00:38:41.400 --> 00:38:43.950
I do not like spiritual manipulation.

00:38:43.960 --> 00:38:45.670
I've seen it done; I worked for some big

00:38:45.680 --> 00:38:49.310
ministries. Don't do this. Don't give

00:38:49.320 --> 00:38:51.590
out of emotion ever.

00:38:51.600 --> 00:38:53.990
Give when the Holy Spirit tugs at

00:38:54.000 --> 00:38:55.070
you.

00:38:55.080 --> 00:38:58.310
Be spirit-led in your giving.

00:38:58.320 --> 00:39:00.390
Listen to the voice of the Spirit of the

00:39:00.400 --> 00:39:04.630
Lord concerning this. There are too

00:39:04.630 --> 00:39:04.640
many

00:39:04.640 --> 00:39:08.710
high notes on the organ

00:39:08.720 --> 00:39:09.950
and you

00:39:11.280 --> 00:39:12.590
say,

00:39:14.040 --> 00:39:15.230
"I feel the Holy Ghost."No,

00:39:15.230 --> 00:39:15.240
you

00:39:15.240 --> 00:39:17.470
didn't feel

00:39:17.480 --> 00:39:18.670
anything.

00:39:18.680 --> 00:39:21.070
This isn't the Holy Ghost;

00:39:21.080 --> 00:39:24.190
it's flesh, and you're being flaky.

00:39:24.200 --> 00:39:26.390
I'm not going to be giving out of

00:39:26.400 --> 00:39:27.830
flakiness.

00:39:27.840 --> 00:39:29.470
I don't care how much you think you

00:39:29.480 --> 00:39:32.030
need for your orphanage or your

00:39:32.040 --> 00:39:34.470
project. You want to play a high note

00:39:34.480 --> 00:39:35.550
on a key

00:39:35.560 --> 00:39:37.630
on your organ to make me feel like I'm

00:39:37.640 --> 00:39:39.910
feeling the Holy Ghost, and you

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:41.750
play the tambourine.

00:39:43.760 --> 00:39:47.670
Sit down.

00:39:47.680 --> 00:39:49.630
It's flaky.

00:39:49.640 --> 00:39:50.990
You're

00:39:51.000 --> 00:39:52.790
all excited and people

00:39:52.790 --> 00:39:52.800
are

00:39:52.800 --> 00:39:54.790
falling out.

00:39:56.120 --> 00:39:57.750
It's flakiness, especially in the

00:39:57.760 --> 00:40:00.070
charismatic circle.

00:40:00.080 --> 00:40:01.270
Stop it.

00:40:03.000 --> 00:40:04.910
I'm telling you all, when

00:40:04.920 --> 00:40:06.350
you're led by the Spirit of God and

00:40:07.680 --> 00:40:09.790
you listen to Him when He tells you

00:40:09.800 --> 00:40:13.070
to give, and you're not emotionally

00:40:13.080 --> 00:40:16.150
being fed some baloney, you're going to

00:40:16.160 --> 00:40:17.750
reap, and God will

00:40:17.760 --> 00:40:20.310
bless you.

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:23.110
Listen again and check it.

00:40:23.120 --> 00:40:24.870
Ask your wife or your

00:40:24.880 --> 00:40:26.470
husband if they feel this way. You may

00:40:26.480 --> 00:40:28.150
not have a husband or wife, but follow

00:40:28.160 --> 00:40:29.910
the Holy Ghost. He'll be your

00:40:29.910 --> 00:40:29.920
guide.

00:40:29.920 --> 00:40:31.510
Listen to

00:40:31.510 --> 00:40:31.520
Him

00:40:31.520 --> 00:40:35.590
and be led by the Spirit of God.

00:40:35.600 --> 00:40:37.870
I'm so tired of charismatic

00:40:37.880 --> 00:40:39.990
flakiness.

00:40:40.000 --> 00:40:41.870
I've

00:40:41.880 --> 00:40:46.390
seen it all.

00:40:46.400 --> 00:40:48.230
People giving their last everything. My

00:40:48.240 --> 00:40:51.270
mom and dad were all hyped

00:40:51.280 --> 00:40:53.590
up in a service one time and gave our

00:40:53.600 --> 00:40:56.750
only car away because they needed

00:40:56.760 --> 00:40:59.510
the building fund paid off. It was our

00:40:59.520 --> 00:41:01.830
only car,

00:41:01.840 --> 00:41:03.190
brand new; my uncle bought it for my

00:41:03.200 --> 00:41:04.950
dad. We were excited to have

00:41:04.960 --> 00:41:06.710
it because it was a little

00:41:06.720 --> 00:41:08.150
Cutlass.

00:41:08.160 --> 00:41:10.310
My dad gave it away because there

00:41:10.310 --> 00:41:10.320
was a

00:41:10.320 --> 00:41:12.270
high note on the keyboard,

00:41:12.280 --> 00:41:13.750
and we suffered. We were freezing in

00:41:13.760 --> 00:41:15.510
the back

00:41:15.520 --> 00:41:17.270
of a truck

00:41:17.280 --> 00:41:20.270
all winter long

00:41:20.280 --> 00:41:21.990
because we didn't have a car to get to

00:41:22.000 --> 00:41:23.590
church

00:41:23.600 --> 00:41:26.110
or school. My dad

00:41:26.120 --> 00:41:27.590
got a camper from my grandparents, and

00:41:27.600 --> 00:41:30.190
it was freezing

00:41:30.200 --> 00:41:32.390
in the negatives. I sat back there with the

00:41:32.400 --> 00:41:34.830
exhaust fumes, mad at

00:41:34.840 --> 00:41:36.830
the church because they took my car since Dad

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:38.230
got hyped

00:41:38.240 --> 00:41:40.190
up about someone giving.

00:41:40.200 --> 00:41:42.590
I've seen it. I've lived it, and it's

00:41:42.600 --> 00:41:45.830
flaky.

00:41:45.840 --> 00:41:49.190
Don't give out of emotion;

00:41:49.200 --> 00:41:53.150
give by the Spirit of God leading you.

00:41:53.160 --> 00:41:54.870
People want to know my opinion about

00:41:54.880 --> 00:41:56.870
it, and I tell you,

00:41:56.880 --> 00:42:00.270
I've seen it all.

00:42:00.280 --> 00:42:01.470
Some of the biggest people in the

00:42:01.480 --> 00:42:03.470
biggest ministries have the biggest planes

00:42:03.470 --> 00:42:03.480
and

00:42:03.480 --> 00:42:05.550
biggest stuff. I don't care if

00:42:05.550 --> 00:42:05.560
they

00:42:05.560 --> 00:42:07.350
have it; I want them to

00:42:07.360 --> 00:42:09.590
be blessed.

00:42:09.600 --> 00:42:11.070
But never

00:42:11.080 --> 00:42:13.470
work on an old lady's emotions to get

00:42:13.480 --> 00:42:16.230
it.

00:42:16.240 --> 00:42:18.870
Let it be spirit-led and God will bless

00:42:18.880 --> 00:42:20.510
your hands.

00:42:21.520 --> 00:42:23.384
That's my message.

00:42:24.400 --> 00:42:26.070
There's a mic drop.

00:42:26.080 --> 00:42:28.030
If you

00:42:28.040 --> 00:42:28.990
listen to what I'm trying to tell you,

00:42:29.000 --> 00:42:30.830
you'll walk in a greater

00:42:30.840 --> 00:42:32.550
side of blessing and you'll have more

00:42:32.560 --> 00:42:33.870
peace

00:42:33.880 --> 00:42:35.190
instead of being ticked off at the

00:42:35.200 --> 00:42:37.030
church

00:42:37.040 --> 00:42:38.670
because

00:42:38.680 --> 00:42:40.430
people are getting mad about

00:42:40.440 --> 00:42:42.230
prosperity.

00:42:44.600 --> 00:42:48.710
Just stay in the right lane.

00:42:48.720 --> 00:42:51.510
Did

00:42:51.520 --> 00:42:53.670
that help at all? Hopefully. I

00:42:53.680 --> 00:42:56.430
talked too long,

00:42:56.440 --> 00:42:57.750
but

00:42:57.760 --> 00:43:00.030
it is what it is. Do

00:43:00.030 --> 00:43:00.040
you

00:43:00.040 --> 00:43:01.990
want to pray now?

00:43:02.000 --> 00:43:03.950
I didn't have anything prepared, but

00:43:03.960 --> 00:43:05.390
the Lord gave you that.

00:43:05.400 --> 00:43:07.350
That came right

00:43:07.360 --> 00:43:09.190
out of the Holy Ghost. I can feel the

00:43:09.200 --> 00:43:11.199
presence of the Lord on it.

00:43:12.160 --> 00:43:15.230
He helped me.

00:43:15.240 --> 00:43:17.910
I just love Him;

00:43:17.920 --> 00:43:22.790
He's my friend. There

00:43:22.790 --> 00:43:22.800
is

00:43:22.800 --> 00:43:26.950
too much flakiness in the church.

00:43:26.950 --> 00:43:26.960
You've

00:43:26.960 --> 00:43:29.950
seen it.

00:43:31.960 --> 00:43:33.910
I know there's a lot of

00:43:33.910 --> 00:43:33.920
corruption

00:43:33.920 --> 00:43:35.830
going on in there, too.

00:43:35.840 --> 00:43:38.030
I could call them all out, but God

00:43:38.040 --> 00:43:39.510
would probably get mad at me, and I'd

00:43:39.520 --> 00:43:42.640
never be on this platform again.

00:43:42.650 --> 00:43:42.670
You'd

00:43:42.680 --> 00:43:44.590
look at me and go, "Brandon,

00:43:44.600 --> 00:43:46.110
what did you just

00:43:46.120 --> 00:43:49.350
say?"because

00:43:49.360 --> 00:43:52.070
there's a lot of sin in there.

00:43:52.080 --> 00:43:55.830
Seriously bad stuff.

00:43:57.280 --> 00:43:59.070
But they are held

00:43:59.080 --> 00:44:01.030
accountable for it on the other side.

00:44:01.040 --> 00:44:03.790
You think you got away with it,

00:44:03.800 --> 00:44:05.790
but

00:44:05.800 --> 00:44:07.790
you didn't.

00:44:07.800 --> 00:44:09.230
You're going to be held accountable for

00:44:11.800 --> 00:44:13.710
everything you thought you did in

00:44:13.720 --> 00:44:14.950
private.

00:44:14.960 --> 00:44:16.750
You're going to stand before the Lord

00:44:16.760 --> 00:44:18.430
one day and give an account for

00:44:19.960 --> 00:44:22.630
how you handled things.

00:44:22.640 --> 00:44:25.630
To whom much is given, much is required.

00:44:28.200 --> 00:44:30.390
I'm more scared for you

00:44:30.400 --> 00:44:32.230
than anything. Some of you

00:44:32.230 --> 00:44:32.240
are

00:44:32.240 --> 00:44:33.630
in

00:44:33.640 --> 00:44:36.550
trouble.

00:44:36.560 --> 00:44:39.110
If people really

00:44:39.120 --> 00:44:41.670
saw the stink behind the stage, they'd

00:44:41.670 --> 00:44:41.680
say,

00:44:41.680 --> 00:44:45.510
"Oh my

00:44:45.520 --> 00:44:46.910
God."Seriously,

00:44:46.920 --> 00:44:48.349
that's why Brandon just stays to

00:44:48.359 --> 00:44:50.750
himself. I don't go into all the big

00:44:50.760 --> 00:44:52.870
preacher circles.

00:44:55.200 --> 00:44:57.030
I go where the Holy Spirit leads me.

00:44:57.960 --> 00:45:00.950
He says, "Go here,

00:45:00.960 --> 00:45:02.990
don't go there. Don't go

00:45:03.000 --> 00:45:05.470
to that platform. Follow

00:45:05.480 --> 00:45:08.430
my voice, son."I

00:45:08.430 --> 00:45:08.440
asked,

00:45:08.440 --> 00:45:09.950
"What about this one?"He said,

00:45:09.960 --> 00:45:14.190
"That's where prophets go to

00:45:14.190 --> 00:45:14.200
die."No

00:45:14.200 --> 00:45:18.230
joke.

00:45:19.960 --> 00:45:21.070
He said that's where

00:45:21.080 --> 00:45:23.511
prophetic voices go to die.

00:45:25.280 --> 00:45:27.710
When He said that, I got chills. I was

00:45:27.720 --> 00:45:30.430
driving down the road. I told Diana,

00:45:30.440 --> 00:45:36.190
"This is what He just

00:45:36.200 --> 00:45:40.590
said."God

00:45:40.600 --> 00:45:43.910
said, "I'm cleaning house in

00:45:43.910 --> 00:45:43.920
2026."First

00:45:43.920 --> 00:45:45.870
Corinthians 5:5 is going to become

00:45:45.880 --> 00:45:48.110
manifest in a great capacity

00:45:48.120 --> 00:45:49.990
for a lot of people. It's

00:45:49.990 --> 00:45:50.000
for

00:45:50.000 --> 00:45:53.190
those who

00:45:53.190 --> 00:45:53.200
touch

00:45:53.200 --> 00:45:55.510
the gold, the glory,

00:45:55.520 --> 00:45:57.950
and the girls.

00:45:57.960 --> 00:45:59.910
Judgment begins in

00:45:59.920 --> 00:46:02.790
my house first. Great TV stations

00:46:02.800 --> 00:46:06.950
will fall, and they will be no more soon.

00:46:06.960 --> 00:46:08.670
You're going to see ministers that you

00:46:08.680 --> 00:46:10.590
thought would be on platforms for the

00:46:10.600 --> 00:46:12.950
rest of their lives who will be no more.

00:46:12.960 --> 00:46:14.550
They'll be like Ananias and

00:46:14.560 --> 00:46:16.470
Sapphira.

00:46:16.480 --> 00:46:17.950
They're gone.

00:46:17.960 --> 00:46:19.310
You're going to go, "What

00:46:19.320 --> 00:46:21.550
happened there?"No explanation. They

00:46:21.560 --> 00:46:23.390
just went.

00:46:23.400 --> 00:46:24.790
Not all of them are bad; some

00:46:24.800 --> 00:46:25.750
are just getting old and need to

00:46:25.760 --> 00:46:27.870
go home.

00:46:30.800 --> 00:46:32.950
But some will.

00:46:32.960 --> 00:46:34.550
Over the next

00:46:34.550 --> 00:46:34.560
three

00:46:34.560 --> 00:46:36.030
years, you're going to see a lot of

00:46:36.040 --> 00:46:37.790
new faces coming up—the new

00:46:37.800 --> 00:46:39.430
Davids, the new Esthers—and you're

00:46:39.440 --> 00:46:41.030
going to see platforms

00:46:41.040 --> 00:46:43.830
explode seemingly out of nowhere.

00:46:43.840 --> 00:46:44.990
You're going to go, "Where in the

00:46:45.000 --> 00:46:47.430
world did they come

00:46:47.430 --> 00:46:47.440
from?"It's

00:46:47.440 --> 00:46:49.750
just the hand of the Lord using

00:46:49.760 --> 00:46:51.430
them because they said, "Here am I,

00:46:51.440 --> 00:46:53.510
Lord, send

00:46:53.510 --> 00:46:53.520
me."And

00:46:53.520 --> 00:46:54.590
you're going to see a lot of the

00:46:54.600 --> 00:46:56.030
people that were somebodies

00:46:56.030 --> 00:46:56.040
and

00:46:56.040 --> 00:46:58.710
such-and-such be nothing.

00:46:58.710 --> 00:46:58.720
It

00:46:58.720 --> 00:47:02.230
will

00:47:02.230 --> 00:47:02.240
be

00:47:02.240 --> 00:47:04.310
just like Saul walking through when the

00:47:04.320 --> 00:47:08.670
anointing was stripped away from him.

00:47:08.670 --> 00:47:08.680
So,

00:47:08.680 --> 00:47:11.630
he rises up a new David to take

00:47:11.640 --> 00:47:13.510
the helm.

00:47:13.520 --> 00:47:16.510
Will you be my new David? He says,

00:47:16.520 --> 00:47:20.990
"Will you be my new person?

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:23.070
Here am I, Lord, send

00:47:23.070 --> 00:47:23.080
me."But

00:47:23.080 --> 00:47:25.070
if I can't handle it,

00:47:25.080 --> 00:47:27.550
and I don't want to ever cause pain to

00:47:27.560 --> 00:47:29.790
any of your people,

00:47:29.800 --> 00:47:33.430
I don't want to be what I have seen.

00:47:33.440 --> 00:47:35.230
If I don't have the character to handle

00:47:35.240 --> 00:47:36.430
the anointing, if I don't have the

00:47:36.440 --> 00:47:38.910
character to handle the platform, don't

00:47:38.920 --> 00:47:41.510
give it to me.

00:47:41.520 --> 00:47:43.390
If I'm going to hurt thousands and

00:47:43.400 --> 00:47:45.070
thousands of people in the future and I

00:47:45.080 --> 00:47:47.270
don't see it,

00:47:47.280 --> 00:47:48.630
please.

00:47:48.640 --> 00:47:50.830
Because it's like what I heard

00:47:50.840 --> 00:47:53.790
Joyce say: the bigger the

00:47:53.800 --> 00:47:56.150
platform, the bigger the level of how

00:47:56.160 --> 00:47:59.110
many people you can hurt.

00:47:59.120 --> 00:48:04.510
And I don't want to hurt people.

00:48:04.520 --> 00:48:05.950
And that's why I say, "Lord,

00:48:05.960 --> 00:48:08.230
create in me a clean heart."Help me stay

00:48:08.240 --> 00:48:10.670
right with you.

00:48:10.680 --> 00:48:13.150
Because it's staying

00:48:13.160 --> 00:48:15.550
on that vine,

00:48:15.560 --> 00:48:18.110
staying on that life source, that's going

00:48:18.120 --> 00:48:20.590
to get you there.

00:48:20.600 --> 00:48:22.630
It's whenever you separate yourself from

00:48:22.640 --> 00:48:25.110
the life source that

00:48:25.120 --> 00:48:27.830
the branch eventually dies. The

00:48:27.840 --> 00:48:30.710
branch doesn't die overnight. Just like

00:48:30.720 --> 00:48:32.830
it is if you prune a tree,

00:48:32.840 --> 00:48:35.920
it dies over time.

